to ensure the rights of vulnerable children are protected is also needed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We have tried to answer these questions through conducting a comprehensive study of the child protection system, the findings of which are presented in this report.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><object class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/The-illusion-of-protection_eng.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Embed of The-illusion-of-protection_eng.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-e5d10782-183d-446e-b593-ee5962764ebe\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/The-illusion-of-protection_eng.pdf\">The-illusion-of-protection_eng<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/The-illusion-of-protection_eng.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-e5d10782-183d-446e-b593-ee5962764ebe\">Download<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Discover what&#8217;s wrong with Ukraine&#8217;s child protection system and why it doesn&#8217;t work in our comprehensive study<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5080,"template":"","tags":[25,51,9],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Report: The illusion of Protection - Hope and Homes<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Discover what&#039;s wrong with Ukraine&#039;s child protection system and why it doesn&#039;t work in our comprehensive study\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/publications\/ukraine-orphanage-system-report-illusion-of-protection\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" c